ars_natura.ritual_desc.ritual_conjure_bi: Creates a biome of beach in a circle around the ritual, converting the area to Beach, Snowy Beach, or Stony Shore biomes.
Creates a cold ocean biome in a circle around the ritual, converting the area to Cold Ocean, Deep Cold Ocean, Frozen Ocean, or Deep Frozen Ocean.
Creates a forest biome in a circle around the ritual, converting the area to Forest, Flower Forest, Dark Forest, Birch Forest, or Old Growth Birch Forest biomes.
Creates a jungle biome in a circle around the ritual, converting the area to Jungle, Bamboo Jungle, or Sparse Jungle biomes.
Creates a mountain biome in a circle around the ritual, converting the area to Meadow, Grove, Cherry Grove, Snowy Slopes, Frozen Peaks, Stony Peaks, or Jagged Peaks biomes.
Creates a desert biome in a circle around the ritual, converting the area to Desert, Badlands, Wooded Badlands, or Eroded Badlands biomes.
Creates a plains biome in a circle around the ritual, converting the area to Plains, Sunflower Plains, Snowy Plains, or Ice Spikes biomes.
Creates an ocean biome in a circle around the ritual, converting the area to Ocean, Deep Ocean, or Mushroom Fields biomes.
Creates a river biome in a circle around the ritual, converting the area to River or Frozen River biomes.
Creates a savanna biome in a circle around the ritual, converting the area to Savanna, Savanna Plateau, or Windswept Savanna biomes.
Creates a swamp biome in a circle around the ritual, converting the area to Swamp or Mangrove Swamp biomes.
Creates a taiga biome in a circle around the ritual, converting the area to Taiga, Snowy Taiga, Old Growth Spruce Taiga, or Old Growth Pine Taiga biomes.
Creates a warm ocean biome in a circle around the ritual, converting the area to Lukewarm Ocean, Warm Ocean, or Deep Lukewarm Ocean.
Creates a windswept hills biome in a circle around the ritual, converting the area to Windswept Hills, Windswept Forest, or Windswept Gravely Hills biomes.
